sequenceDiagram
    participant User as Data Scientist
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API Server<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant Webhook as Validating Webhook<br/>9443/TCP HTTPS
    participant Operator as OGX K8s Operator<br/>(controller-runtime)
    participant Kustomize as Kustomize Engine
    participant OGXPod as OGX Server Pod<br/>8321/TCP HTTP
    participant Provider as Remote Inference Provider<br/>(vLLM/OpenAI/Azure/etc.)<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant VectorDB as Vector DB<br/>(PGVector/Milvus/Qdrant)
    participant S3 as S3 Storage<br/>443/TCP HTTPS

    Note over User,S3: Flow 1: OGXServer Reconciliation

    User->>K8sAPI: kubectl apply OGXServer CR<br/>Auth: kubeconfig
    K8sAPI->>Webhook: Validate OGXServer<br/>POST /validate-ogx-io-v1beta1-ogxserver<br/>mTLS (API server cert)
    Webhook-->>K8sAPI: Admission Response (allow/deny)
    K8sAPI-->>User: CR created/rejected

    K8sAPI->>Operator: Watch event: OGXServer created<br/>HTTPS TLS 1.2+ / SA token
    Operator->>Kustomize: Render manifests from base templates<br/>Apply plugin pipeline (namespace, prefix, fields)
    Kustomize-->>Operator: Rendered K8s resources

    Operator->>K8sAPI: Create Deployment, Service, NetworkPolicy,<br/>PVC, HPA, PDB, ConfigMap, Ingress<br/>HTTPS 443/TCP / SA token
    K8sAPI-->>Operator: Resources created

    Operator->>OGXPod: Health check: GET /v1/providers<br/>HTTP 8321/TCP
    OGXPod-->>Operator: Provider info
    Operator->>OGXPod: Version check: GET /v1/version<br/>HTTP 8321/TCP
    OGXPod-->>Operator: Version info

    Operator->>K8sAPI: Update OGXServer status<br/>HTTPS 443/TCP / SA token

    Note over User,S3: Flow 2: OGX Server Inference Request

    User->>OGXPod: POST inference request<br/>HTTP/HTTPS {port}/TCP<br/>Auth: Application-level
    OGXPod->>Provider: Forward to remote provider<br/>HTTPS 443/TCP TLS 1.2+<br/>Auth: API key / IAM credentials
    Provider-->>OGXPod: Inference response
    OGXPod->>VectorDB: Vector I/O query<br/>TCP / Configurable TLS<br/>Auth: Password/Token
    VectorDB-->>OGXPod: Vector results
    OGXPod->>S3: File storage access<br/>HTTPS 443/TCP TLS 1.2+<br/>Auth: AWS credentials
    S3-->>OGXPod: File data
    OGXPod-->>User: Inference response

    Note over User,S3: Flow 3: Legacy Adoption Migration

    User->>K8sAPI: Create OGXServer CR with adoption annotations<br/>(ogx.io/adopt-storage, ogx.io/adopt-networking)
    K8sAPI->>Operator: Watch event: OGXServer with adoption
    Operator->>K8sAPI: Scale legacy LlamaStackDistribution Deployment to 0<br/>HTTPS 443/TCP / SA token
    Operator->>K8sAPI: Relabel PVCs, update Service selectors,<br/>transfer Ingress ownership<br/>HTTPS 443/TCP / SA token
    K8sAPI-->>Operator: Resources adopted
    Operator->>K8sAPI: Update OGXServer status with adoption timestamps
